{
  "page": "Battle in the hills below the Golden Tooth",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Battle in the hills below the Golden Tooth</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Conflict</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">War of the Five Kings</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Date</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/298_AC\" title=\"298 AC\">298&#160;AC</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\nbeneath the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Tooth\" title=\"Golden Tooth\">Golden Tooth</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">Westerlands</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Result</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">Lannister</a> victory</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%; text-align:left;\">\n<tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Combatants</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tully\" title=\"House Tully\"><img alt=\"House Tully.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/61/House_Tully.svg/32px-House_Tully.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/61/House_Tully.svg/48px-House_Tully.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/61/House_Tully.svg/64px-House_Tully.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">Riverlands</a>, led by <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tully\" title=\"House Tully\">House Tully</a>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Piper\" title=\"House Piper\"><img alt=\"House Piper.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/3b/House_Piper.svg/20px-House_Piper.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/3b/House_Piper.svg/30px-House_Piper.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/3b/House_Piper.svg/40px-House_Piper.svg.png 2x\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/index.php/House_Piper\" title=\"House Piper\">House Piper</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Vance_of_Wayfarer%27s_Rest\" title=\"House Vance of Wayfarer&#39;s Rest\"><img alt=\"House Vance of Wayfarer&#39;s Rest.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/House_Vance_of_Wayfarer%27s_Rest.svg/20px-House_Vance_of_Wayfarer%27s_Rest.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/House_Vance_of_Wayfarer%27s_Rest.svg/30px-House_Vance_of_Wayfarer%27s_Rest.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/House_Vance_of_Wayfarer%27s_Rest.svg/40px-House_Vance_of_Wayfarer%27s_Rest.svg.png 2x\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/index.php/House_Vance_of_Wayfarer%27s_Rest\" title=\"House Vance of Wayfarer&#39;s Rest\">House Vance of Wayfarer's Rest</a></li></ul></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\"><img alt=\"House Lannister.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/32px-House_Lannister.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/48px-House_Lannister.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/64px-House_Lannister.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">Westerlands</a>, led by <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Jaime_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Jaime-1\">&#91;N 1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Commanders</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Piper\" title=\"House Piper\"><img alt=\"House Piper.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/3b/House_Piper.svg/20px-House_Piper.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/3b/House_Piper.svg/30px-House_Piper.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/3b/House_Piper.svg/40px-House_Piper.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Clement_Piper\" title=\"Clement Piper\">Clement Piper</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/House_Vance_of_Wayfarer%27s_Rest\" title=\"House Vance of Wayfarer&#39;s Rest\"><img alt=\"House Vance of Wayfarer&#39;s Rest.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/House_Vance_of_Wayfarer%27s_Rest.svg/20px-House_Vance_of_Wayfarer%27s_Rest.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/House_Vance_of_Wayfarer%27s_Rest.svg/30px-House_Vance_of_Wayfarer%27s_Rest.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/House_Vance_of_Wayfarer%27s_Rest.svg/40px-House_Vance_of_Wayfarer%27s_Rest.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Vance\" title=\"Lord Vance\">Lord Vance</a></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\"><img alt=\"Kingsguard.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/20px-Kingsguard.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/30px-Kingsguard.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/40px-Kingsguard.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Strength</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">Armies of Houses <a href=\"/index.php/House_Piper\" title=\"House Piper\">Piper</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Vance_of_Wayfarer%27s_Rest\" title=\"House Vance of Wayfarer&#39;s Rest\">Vance</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Frey_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Frey-2\">&#91;N 2&#93;</a></sup></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      ~15,000<sup id=\"cite_ref-Horse_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Horse-3\">&#91;N 3&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Casualties</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">Complete<br /><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Vance\" title=\"Lord Vance\">Lord Vance</a>†</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      unknown</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>A <b>battle in the hills below the Golden Tooth</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> is the opening battle of the <a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">War of the Five Kings</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">Lannister</a> campaign in the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Prelude\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Prelude</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Battle\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Battle</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Aftermath\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Aftermath</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Prelude\">Prelude</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Battle_in_the_hills_below_the_Golden_Tooth&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Prelude\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Edmure_Tully\" title=\"Edmure Tully\">Edmure Tully</a> finds out that the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">Lannisters</a> are raising a host at <a href=\"/index.php/Casterly_Rock\" title=\"Casterly Rock\">Casterly Rock</a>. With Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Hoster_Tully\" title=\"Hoster Tully\">Hoster Tully</a> ill, Edmure sends riders to the Rock, demanding that Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a> proclaim his intent. Meanwhile, he starts raising a host at <a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a> and sends <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Vance\" title=\"Lord Vance\">Lord Vance</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Wayfarer%27s_Rest\" title=\"Wayfarer&#39;s Rest\">Wayfarer's Rest</a> and Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Clement_Piper\" title=\"Clement Piper\">Clement Piper</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Pinkmaiden\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Pinkmaiden\">Pinkmaiden</a> to guard the pass below the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Tooth\" title=\"Golden Tooth\">Golden Tooth</a>, to prevent any Lannister armies from entering the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Tywin dispatches Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Gregor_Clegane\" title=\"Gregor Clegane\">Gregor Clegane</a> to raid the villages along the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Fork\" title=\"Red Fork\">Red Fork</a>, and Gregor circumvents the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tully\" title=\"House Tully\">Tully</a> forces below the Golden Tooth. In response Edmure further divides his forces, sending men to every village and holdfast within a day's ride of the border. Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a>, fears this will weaken the defense of the riverlands.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Battle\">Battle</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Battle_in_the_hills_below_the_Golden_Tooth&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Battle\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a>, commanding the Lannister forces, descends on the outnumbered <a href=\"/index.php/Rivermen\" title=\"Rivermen\">rivermen</a> and breaks them. Lord Vance is slain during the fight and Lord Piper retreats back to <a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a> with the remnants of his forces, with Jaime following on his heels. Meanwhile, Tywin brings another Lannister army up from the south.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Aftermath\">Aftermath</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Battle_in_the_hills_below_the_Golden_Tooth&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Aftermath\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The rout of the rivermen beneath the Golden Tooth allows Jaime to then fight the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_under_the_walls_of_Riverrun\" title=\"Battle under the walls of Riverrun\">battle under the walls of Riverrun</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot59.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot59.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Marq_Piper\" title=\"Marq Piper\">Marq Piper</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Karyl_Vance\" title=\"Karyl Vance\">Karyl Vance</a>, now a lord, raid behind the Lannisters' lines.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> Jaime later thinks of the battle as a glorious victory.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Battle_in_the_hills_below_the_Golden_Tooth&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Less than a fortnight past, they fought a battle in the hills below the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Tooth\" title=\"Golden Tooth\">Golden Tooth</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Edmure_Tully\" title=\"Edmure Tully\">Uncle Edmure</a> had sent <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Vance\" title=\"Lord Vance\">Lord Vance</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Clement_Piper\" title=\"Clement Piper\">Lord Piper</a> to hold the pass, but the Kingslayer descended on them and put them to flight. Lord Vance was slain. The last word we had was that Lord Piper was falling back to join your brother and his other bannermen at <a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a>, with <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a> on his heels.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">Robb Stark</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Your brother</a> has been covering himself with glory.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>On the morning after the battle, the <a href=\"/index.php/Crow\" title=\"Crow\">crows</a> had feasted on victors and vanquished alike, as once they had feasted on <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaegar_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaegar Targaryen\">Rhaegar Targaryen</a> after <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Trident\" title=\"Battle of the Trident\">the Trident</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Notes\">Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Battle_in_the_hills_below_the_Golden_Tooth&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Jaime-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Jaime_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Houses <a href=\"/index.php/House_Banefort\" title=\"House Banefort\">Banefort</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Brax\" title=\"House Brax\">Brax</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Crakehall\" title=\"House Crakehall\">Crakehall</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Estren\" title=\"House Estren\">Estren</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Greenfield\" title=\"House Greenfield\">Greenfield</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Prester\" title=\"House Prester\">Prester</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Westerling\" title=\"House Westerling\">Westerling</a> are not directly mentioned in the fighting below the Golden Tooth. However, as men from these houses are part of <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a>'s host in the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_in_the_Whispering_Wood\" title=\"Battle in the Whispering Wood\">Whispering Wood</a> and at <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Camps\" title=\"Battle of the Camps\">Riverrun</a>, they may be present at the Golden Tooth.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Frey-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Frey_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">With the Pipers and Vances the only houses involved, the rivermen army must at least be far below 8,000 men, as <a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\">House Frey</a>, the strongest bannermen of the riverlands, can only field 4,000 men on their own.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Horse-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Horse_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">After <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_under_the_walls_of_Riverrun\" title=\"Battle under the walls of Riverrun\">capturing Edmure</a>, Jaime besieges Riverrun with 12,000 foot and 2,000 or 3,000 horse, according to <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_63\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 63\">Chapter 63</a>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Battle_in_the_hills_below_the_Golden_Tooth&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-2\">1.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_55\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 55\">Chapter 55</a>, Catelyn VIII.</span>\n</li>\n<li